  "title": "🥗 Dietetic Technician #HHLT",
  "description": "<p>💰 Salary: $2,500 – $3,000</p><p>Working Hours: Mon - Fri, 8.30am - 6pm</p><p>Queenstown<br /><br /><br /></p><p>🌟 Job Scope</p><p>Support Dietitians and Manager in administrative and nutrition-related tasks</p><p>Assist in preparing nutrition education materials, slides, and programmes</p><p>Handle patient appointment booking, reminders, and basic pre-clerking</p><p>Perform nutritional analysis using computer software</p><p>Manage oral nutrition supplement (ONS) samples and ensure proper tracking</p><p>Update department website, records, and reports</p><p>Assist with data entry, statistics, and research support</p><p>Answer phone calls and handle general enquiries<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>✅ Requirements</p><p>Minimum Diploma in Applied Food Science and Nutrition</p><p>Comfortable with administrative and clerical work</p><p>Good communication and customer service skills</p><p>Proficient in Microsoft Word, Excel, and PowerPoint<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>If interested, please email me at biopharma@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
